For config file:
```
<main>
   key1
   key2 value2
</main>

```

python parser is parsing into
```
{  
   "main":{  
      "key1":"key2 value2"
   }
}
```

while perl parse will parse into
```
{  
   "main" => {  
      "key1"=> undef,
      "key2"=> "value2"
   }
}
```

Can this be handled?

